ame ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb12225">Mell, Max</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1906-10-26_01">Schnitzler an Mell, 26. 10. 1906</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1907-07-15_01">Mell an Schnitzler, 15. 7. 1907</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
